Cultivate Innovative and Leadership Abilities in order to Develop Therapeutic Skills and Professional Research 

課程概述 Course Description
       經由介紹特定國家職能治療(occupational therapy, OT)之發展，以開展同學之國際視野並掌握專業發展史，以及介紹或訪問模範資深職能治療師及學校教師，讓同學瞭解臨床職能治療師與教師之生涯發展，以利同學進行生涯規畫。The course is to broaden the perspectives of OT students and provide students with role models for future OT career development. The course includes (1) lectures and discussion on the development of OT in specific countries; (2) student seminars on the development of OT in other countries; (3) role-model speeches and discussions by experienced university teachers and outstanding clinicians in OT; and (4) student reports on interviews of other experienced university teachers and outstanding clinicians. 
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
瞭解特定國家之OT發展、里程碑與挑戰瞭解特定國家之OT學制特點與展望開展OT世界觀瞭解特定模範資深職能治療師之生涯發展歷程、成就與挑戰瞭解特定模範資深大學職能治療教師之生涯發展歷程、成就與挑戰具OT生涯規畫/發展之參考典範 

